</div>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#ffffcc; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h4 id="toc3"><span>NOTIFICATION</span></h4>
<p><tt>You have a new urgent message.</tt></p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>FROM:</strong> Researcher Madeleine Sailer<br />
<strong>TO:</strong> Dr. Christopher Erwick</p>
<p>Alright, Chris, I need your help. That work I was assigned to? I found out something I wasn't supposed to. I'm in trouble and I can't get out of it, not this time. I need a favour and it has to be a big one. We have known each other for the longest time and I trust you. It won't be easy, if it was, I would ask someone else to do it. I have done a lot for you over the past 20 years and you have done a lot for me. Please help me with this.<br />
Kill me.</p>
</blockquote>
<table class="wiki-content-table">
